BT /F1 10 Tf 60 468 Td (simplified Greater Cairo road network. The project combines classical graph algorithms,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 60 454 Td (dynamic programming, greedy optimization, machine learning, and interactive visualization) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 60 440 Td (into one Streamlit web application.) Tj ET
