BT /F1 10 Tf 60 609 Td (Each node includes an ID, name, type, population, longitude, and latitude. Each edge) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 60 595 Td (includes source node, destination node, distance, capacity, condition, and construction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 60 581 Td (cost. Existing roads have zero construction cost, while potential future roads have a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 60 567 Td (positive construction cost.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 60 547 Td (The Streamlit application loads the graph once using a cached function. This improves) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 60 533 Td (performance because the graph and machine learning predictor do not need to be rebuilt on) Tj ET
